##  Scholarship and Internship Opportunities
In partnership with Scholarship America, Amazon Future Engineer provides 100 students from underrepresented and underserved communities with $10,000/year scholarships. After their freshman year, scholars go on to become interns at Amazon. This opportunity supports college students early in their career path while also giving them the chance to apply their CS skills in a practical setting. 

