## Preparation Classes and Resources for High School Students
Amazon Future Engineer will also provide more than 2,000 schools that serve students from underrepresented and underserved communities across the country with Intro to Computer Science and AP Computer Science classes through curriculum providers. Amazon’s funding provides preparatory lessons, tutorials, professional development for teachers, fully sequenced and paced digital curriculum for students, and live online support every day of the week for both teachers and students. 

## Free CSTA+ Membership
Take your teaching to the next level with a CSTA+ membership sponsored by Amazon Future Engineer. You’ll receive monthly educational resources like members-only webinars and newsletters, priority access and discounts to CSTA+ conferences and events, and free or discounted teaching aids and online courses.

